e gold of the buddha.&#xA0;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-584x810.jpg\" alt=\"Wat Tham Sua krabi\"><\/noscript><img width=\"244\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Wat Tham Sua krabi\" class=\"wp-image-20980 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-584x810.jpg 584w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-300x416.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-600x832.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-433x600.jpg 433w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-244x338.jpg 244w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-1107x1536.jpg 1107w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-130x180.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-554x768.jpg 554w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-738x1024.jpg 738w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121812\/Wat-Tham-Sua-krabi-779x1080.jpg 779w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23