iv>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>5. Krabi Night Market<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The night market in Krabi Town is one of the best in the country! Every Friday, Saturday and Sunday at 5 PM, the market opens its doors, featuring stalls selling traditional Thai street foods and goods. Get a delicious dinner at one, or multiple, stalls and enjoy it in the center court with live music.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do krabi\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do krabi\" class=\"wp-image-20823 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121848\/best-things-to-do-krabi-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/2