 a direct ferry (7 hours) from Krabi Town. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/koh-lipe\/krabi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Get tickets here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book your transportation tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand.jpg\" alt=\"best time travel thailand\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"304\" alt=\"best time travel thailand\" class=\"wp-image-20987 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand-600x405.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand-800x540.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand-1080x728.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121801\/best-time-travel-thailand-450x304.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-